The paper discusses the problem of symbol emergence in cognitive developmental systems, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of artificial intelligence, machine learning, robotics, and systems engineering. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
